data.description: Spectacular home located on a circle with small park across the street. Recently remodeled kitchen to include counter tops, appliances and new tile backsplash. Tons of counter space and adjacent dining space large enough for table for 8! Huge primary suite with bay window and vaulted ceilings and separate exit. Jack-n-Jill bath shared with 3rd bedroom. Large living room with saltillo tile flooring and shutters on the windows. Amazing back patio with storage area overlooking the pool.  Great hang-out area off of the back patio. 12x12 workshop/storage. Super location with no HOA!
